{"tid":1837540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完韓國<<流感>>電影  預見到武漢肺炎既境況","createTime":"2020-01-23T16:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T13:45:54.000Z","uid":80017,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"22d67b09b0ba66b1e582c15b13169aa26e0d9f54","tid":1837540,"uid":80017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/njyeD7T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnjyeD7T.jpg&h=b259a4eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2013年上映的韓國災難恐怖電影，講述一種由非法移民所帶來的致命流感在韓國盆唐區爆發後，使所有感染者會死於36小時內而引發混亂，而被隔離於城市裏無法逃脫的人們，開始為生存而掙扎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源東南亞人用貨櫃箱偷渡去韓國，之後接頭人去到時，發現箱入面啲人感染病毒死哂，得翻一個<span style=\"color: green;\">生還者</span>(佢有抗體，不過後尾走甩左，要全城大搜捕佢整疫苗) 。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8vTUP6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8vTUP6.jpg&h=74cb38f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接頭人亦因爲接觸過死者感染左病毒，於是係個城市度四圍咳將啲病毒四圍傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjQdakn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjQdakn.jpg&h=58d9d781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然政府輕視左呢隻病毒以後係普通流感，到發現啲人無啦啦係街會咳到嘔血，又撞車又死人，搞到個城一片混亂，先肯公佈<span style=\"color: red;\">封鎖城市，隔離疫者</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5k5dajy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5k5dajy.jpg&h=bb01b19d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VpDaW0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVpDaW0e.jpg&h=7f4e7e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNmLLTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNmLLTA.jpg&h=14fe8a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2Zp1sW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2Zp1sW.jpg&h=00089703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n套戲有好多人性的表現，而當中最令我深刻既就係呢個<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">公仔鉗</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CKjmjcO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCKjmjcO.png&h=450ce62b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">唔劇透咁多喇，想知個鉗究竟住啲乜，自己線上看<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.139mov.com/vod/14/16558play.html?16558-0-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.139mov.com%2Fvod%2F14%2F16558play.html%3F16558-0-1&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=0c550114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.139mov.com/vod/14/16558play.html?16558-0-1</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年SARS中國封鎖消息都未話要<span style=\"color: red;\">封城</span>咁嚴重，依家要<span style=\"color: red;\">封城</span>肯定係爆到七彩一發不可收拾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於點樣對待未死又就黎死啲支那人？我希望係用呢個<span style=\"color: blue;\">公仔鉗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQDY5VR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQDY5VR.png&h=26d851e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，記得帶口罩啊各位！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1b434ca34e86a430f353083bd1408af3769ecb38","tid":1837540,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人爭氣啦</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外媒仲日日報香港 - task1 <br />\n國際日日插中共 - task2<br />\n全部唔上千rt  點搞呀</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter組24小時keep住更新</span></strong><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=05bcb2ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"99870d1e9904b3898274b1fd452d93f13ece8cb3","tid":1837540,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"快少少 好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a35f08feaf72806a65909e877b73bb266fa5b7c","tid":1837540,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e9f856b87d1fce4c878e92eed1d0cfcd8e676b","tid":1837540,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"留名等睇夾夾機出場"},{"pid":"43b12a04af1aa0a8ade02e4a6b26a85d97630057","tid":1837540,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"夾死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d53fd22b28400108650308a7844e8dcae444c40","tid":1837540,"uid":15305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43b12a04af1aa0a8ade02e4a6b26a85d97630057","tid":1837540,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"夾死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><